{"tid":2166027,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"增強速度1979年以來最快","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T07:43:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76e84b864a2bc79e64d5d17452d2fe4187a5015e","tid":2166027,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/2TU5LD76UZHGBJ62SVK5AVEW6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F2TU5LD76UZHGBJ62SVK5AVEW6M%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5b%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=b63b80ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F2TU5LD76UZHGBJ62SVK5AVEW6M%2F&h=9e747875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/2TU5LD76UZHGBJ62SVK5AVEW6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n增強速度1979年以來最快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZGWnSCnflAOkvHbelpj6ykZCFOA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XMA6JZ5ASBG7ZM5XHCMATGXQ6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZGWnSCnflAOkvHbelpj6ykZCFOA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXMA6JZ5ASBG7ZM5XHCMATGXQ6U.jpg&h=496d62d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【沙田】■經過一夜狂風暴雨，昨日城門河的水位上升不少。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海高斯來去匆匆，由一號升級至九號風球不足22小時，是有紀錄以來第四快，亦殺港人一個措手不及。天文台稱，海高斯迅速增強，主要因海水溫暖、微弱垂直風切變及良好的高空輻散三大因素影響。<br />\n<br />\n22小時內變九號波<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QIqWnZYtMzcz70JboLfmJEvZ0PA=/620x1270/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FHLZWHQHU5HFTLPJF7DMXQ4CGI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQIqWnZYtMzcz70JboLfmJEvZ0PA%3D%2F620x1270%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFHLZWHQHU5HFTLPJF7DMXQ4CGI.gif&h=3e482e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次是繼2018年9月超強颱風「山竹」襲港後，本港再掛起九號風球。海高斯襲港期間，由前日凌晨3時40分天文台發出一號戒備信號，至昨晨1時30分改發九號烈風或暴風增強信號，僅經歷21小時50分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n天文台高級科學主任李細明稱，海高斯比預期增強得快和來得近，主要因為海水溫暖、微弱垂直風切變及良好的高空輻散等有利氣象條件影響，令海高斯「快高長大」，一日內由低壓區升級成颱風。<br />\n<br />\n根據天文台資料，海高斯是第四個以最短時間，由一號風球升至九號風球的颱風，最快是1949年9月一個無名颱風，僅在13小時15分鐘內升級。<br />\n<br />\n有分析指，海高斯來襲期間，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"05cbabb35458550d2e5ed907fc1671ce32c6222b","tid":2166027,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"無名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a10dc7399ad5cc7567fc602eaaba0ad8d9bbed","tid":2166027,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"積咗好耐"},{"pid":"b87666bb20a9c691f6d91c6bd38b0fea43444e95","tid":2166027,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"李氏力場影響力亦起碼佔左20年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾無未試過放8號風球假<br />\n一係夜晚8點掛, 5點落波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c895546310a54fea8d1f87c6fa9588d34a0b518d","tid":2166027,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"呢個係加速時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}